Showroom Manager
- ,
Gold Career Provider
This employer achieved a Gold Career Provider status based on their record of hiring on Bayt.com.
Date Posted: 2014/05/02 23:00:24
Ref. JB3046661
Job Description
Develops and manages a sales budge operation for the showroom, and also develops and achieves budget for the showroom to increase company sales and profitability. To develop and lead the showroom team by hiring, trinaing, coaching and providing feedback to the management as well as the associates. The ideal candidate is expected to be an automobile enthusiast showing great level of energy towards customers and the organization.
Skills
- Hire, train, supervise, assist and evaluate showroom sales associates.
- Plan and coordinate installation of new displays.
- Coordinate special events sponsored by showroom.
- Participate as marketing member.
- Monitor showroom KPIs / MIS.
Education
BA
